snippet.title: What's the Hoot? Ep. 1 | Amber KB Wilson
snippet.description:
What's up everyone!

Welcome to the very first video of "What's the Hoot?" a video series focused on givin' a hoot for mentorship. There's so many people out there who haven't been exposed to mentorship, and it's our job to tell you what's all the hoot about mentorship.

In this first episode, we have one of my fellow ambassadors, Amber KB Wilson. During this talk, we chat about our favorite moments of being mentored, and discuss why mentorship can also lead to friendship. Pull out your notebooks because we droppin' the hoot on this one!

If you would like to connect with Amber, check out her socials below and if you enjoy this content, consider subscribing to the YouTube channel!

+++
Amber's LinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/in/amberkbwilson/

+++
Connect with mentors on ADPList: https://adplist.org

Follow me on:
LinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/in/jasonacasimiro/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/jason.in.ux/
Medium: https://jason-casimiro7.medium.com

And of course, subscribe if you enjoy this content!
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCyF8emVa_1K88A4ydreIedA
